<p rend="chapter">Rudhādayo</p>

<p rend="hangnum" n="101"><hi rend="paranum">101</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi></p>

<p rend="gatha1"> Rudhi āvaraṇe muca mocane rica recane,</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Sica seke yuja yoge bhuja pālanabhojane;</p>

<p rend="hangnum" n="102"><hi rend="paranum">102</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi></p>

<p rend="gatha1"> Katicchede chidi dvedhākaraṇe bhida vidāraṇe</p>

<p rend="gatha2">Vida lābhe lupacchede vināse lipalimpane</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Pisa saṃcuṇṇane hisi vihiṃsāyaṃ (rudhādayo;)</p>
